    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver for anyone looking for functional transportation without the premium price tag. The engine and transmission are in good working order, and the car handles well on the road. However, please note that there are visible cosmetic imperfections, including some scratches on the exterior and minor wear on the interior upholstery. It has been maintained for basic functionality, though it may require some minor upcoming maintenance typical for its age. Overall, it is a solid, road-worthy vehicle that is ready for its next owner.",
